Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.38,0:01:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今天的味噌汤是两位的闺女做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}希望爸爸妈妈会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}看上去就不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:47.76,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}早安 鹫尾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}妈妈 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}奇怪 我不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.22,0:02:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乃木 你在教室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而且马上就是晨会了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫尾 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}各位同学 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}早安！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三之轮银同学 你迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:29.28,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好痛 很痛耶老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赶快就座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三三还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小银 你今天怎么迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}升上六年级总会有不少事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}忘记带课本了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今天的值日生是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}起立
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们能来这里 都是托神树大人的福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}向神龛敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们该完成使命了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我还是第一次见到呢 原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神树大人的结界？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.52,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs105\pos(591,300)\alpha&HFF&\t(0,300,0\alpha&F00&)}第{\r\blur3\fs105\alpha&HFF&\t(200,500,0\alpha&F00&)}一{\r\blur3\fs105\alpha&HFF&\t(400,700,0\alpha&F00&)}集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.52,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\alpha&HFF&\t(0,300,0\alpha&F00&)\move(930,720,960,750,0,400)}鹫{\r\blur3\alpha&HFF&\t(200,500,0\alpha&F00&)}尾{\r\blur3\alpha&HFF&\t(400,700,0\alpha&F00&)}須{\r\blur3\alpha&HFF&\t(600,900,0\alpha&F00&)}美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这就是神树大人做出的结界内的世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}树海…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}跟听到的一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好壮观 全都是树耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那是大桥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大概就是那个没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}连接起这里与墙壁外的桥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}敌人会从那里袭击过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好兴奋 我们竟然成了勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三之轮 这可不是说着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那就是敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那家伙跨过大桥 到达神树大人身边时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}世界就会不复存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}得由我们阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来完成使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}苍茫天地中 森罗万象拂吾身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神明驻吾心 遵吾意愿现世间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}献吾之精魂 万丈神力齐相助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}献吾之精魂 承蒙圣力御外敌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我的第一次实战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过我们还没有做配合训练呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为敌人出现的时间比神谕提及的更早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过应该没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小心应付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好 干掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三三 我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们都站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:08:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好宽敞 跟训练时完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想不到这里原本是城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真是太奇妙了 鹫尾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}从另一侧来袭的家伙 Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}击退敌人所花的时间越长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}原本的世界就会受到越大的负面影响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三三
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}两位！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.83,0:09:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}看我一斧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想起来这个可以当盾用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}跟强烈台风一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:09:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫尾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这种敌人要怎么对付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:10:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我的弓箭伤害不够
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三之轮力气不小 但难以近身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乃木连我都不知道怎么应付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到底该如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不行动起来就危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三之轮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}弹性好强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三三 你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}居然全喝下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是获得了神力的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}把水喝干不费吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三三 你好厉害 有味道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一开始是汽水 喝着喝着变成乌龙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}听上去并不好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}现在要紧的是Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那家伙很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}分身神灵太多了 肯定离出口不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们追击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但刚才的攻击没有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但不快点 它就要跑出大桥了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}它要是跑出去 就没办法击退了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}拿出斗志再战一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我突然有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}它发现我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.51,0:12:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}转来我们这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}得抓紧时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}展开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这把长枪能变化成盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}园子真是万能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}顶着盾牌前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乃木 撑得住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}勇者要看斗志 把它顶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一二 一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来 鹫尾也跟着喊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一二 一二 一二 一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}突击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫尾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好难瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三三 我把你甩过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三之轮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三三
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}尝到厉害了没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}镇魂之仪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三三 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 我狠狠地给它吃了一顿斧头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}多亏有你 仪式开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}平息下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}击退…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}原来我们不会直接回学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}糟了 还穿着室内鞋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}刚才拍到树海了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}哎 照片不是树海了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}看来是拍不下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喂 鹫尾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}须美？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}须美助？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只是险胜而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果只有我一个人 就输定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.57,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs45\1c&H545454&\frx356\fry6\frz5.832\pos(375,444)}【没有朋友】如何与人交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.57,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H545454&\frz5.832\pos(408,597)\frx356\fry2}「没有朋友…」这种心情很痛苦呢。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.57,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H545454&\frx356\fry2\pos(462,900)\frz6.678}我教你几招教你交朋友的方法吧吧♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.57,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\b0\fs45\1c&H6938F2&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frx356\fry2\frz6.678\pos(516,969)}3{\shad3\bord3\1c&HC6DAD9&\3c&H3B4C4F&\4c&H3B4C4F&}大妙招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}昨天也跟各位同学说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这三位同学肩负着神树大人指派的重要使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以她们会像昨天那样 突然从教室消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到时候不要慌张慌乱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}静下心来 默默为她们三个加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}同学们还是要以平日的课业为重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}使命很辛苦吗 受了伤很痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这可不能告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小气鬼～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:29.07,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}告诉我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乃木 三之轮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可以的话…我们去开个庆功宴…好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:18:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我…我对平安迎来今天 感到由衷的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在这美好的一天我宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神世纪298年 勇者初战告捷庆功宴正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}祝在座的各位身体健康 学业有成 前途无量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.19,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太死板了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.48,0:18:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢你 须美助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我之前也好几次想邀请你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但没能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以超开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是鹫尾第一次主动邀请我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}确实如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}都还没配合演练过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但我们第一场战斗打得真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也很兴奋 有好多想说的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也是 想要和你们说说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以邀请了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我以前不是很信任你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}并不是说我讨厌你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只是我不习惯依赖他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}须美助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但这样是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果…只有我一个人 肯定什么都办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为有你们在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那个…所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我能跟你们当朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们不是已经是了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好开心 我也好想和须美助当朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}其实我也不太会交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}原来须美助的想法跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:20:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好开心呀 须美助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那个…乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你怎么突然用须美助叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不知不觉就帮你取了个绰号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你自己都没自觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高兴是高兴啦 但我不太喜欢这个绰号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那鹫娜怎么样 很有偶像的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}更不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}乃木也不喜欢「园琳琳」这种叫法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不起 当我没说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想到了 你觉得「鹫鹫」怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那就这样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}请多指教 鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好 那你们就叫我银吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「三之轮」听上去好见外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来庆祝交上朋友的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家一起去吃这里超赞的冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}选择焙茶‧可尔必思口味太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三三你的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}酱油蚕豆口味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那是什么口味 不过看上去挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}抹茶淡淡的苦编织出的口味 真是绝妙的搭配
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那么好吃的话 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这种事我是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好吃 这就是第一次配合工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}用词很会让人想歪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.08,0:22:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}早就想跟朋友做一次这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.23,0:22:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}鹫鹫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好开心呀
Comment: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,OP-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:19.58,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}キミを連れて駆け出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:22.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}誰も追いつけない場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:27.69,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}今こそ叶えようよ　あの日のやくそく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:42.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}片隅の幸せのつぼみ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:45.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}銀色に輝いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:48.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}咲いたら見せてあげよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:53.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}見返したアルバムの中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:56.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}その頃も今もそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:58.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}一緒に笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:04.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}南のほうから染まっていく季節
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:07.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}ただいまと言ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.29,0:23:10.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}きっとすぐに迎えに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:12.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}キミを連れて駆け出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:15.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}誰も追いつけない場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:20.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}今こそ叶えようよ　あの日のやくそく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:26.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}ねえ　ずっと待ってたよ　キミのことを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:32.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}おかえり　私をもう二度と置いてかないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:19.58,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}牵起你的手 迈开脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:22.19,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}去那片没有人能够追上的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:27.69,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}让我们在这里 实现那一天许下的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:42.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}吐露在角落里的 一株幸福的花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:45.49,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}闪耀着银露的光泽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.49,0:22:48.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}等它绽放 就让我带你来看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:53.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}翻来覆去过的这本相册
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:56.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}记录着那个时候 还有今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:58.91,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}我们纯真的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:04.70,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}南方吹来的春风 为世界染上了绿意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:07.29,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}记得说声「我回来了」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.29,0:23:10.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}我一定三步并作两步迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:12.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}牵起你的手 迈开脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:15.71,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}去那片没有人能够追上的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:20.96,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}让我们在这里 实现那一天许下的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.96,0:23:26.17,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}你知道吗 我一直等待着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:32.81,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur7.5}欢迎回来 可不要再丢下我独自启程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神世纪298年 这是三位勇者交织成的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是被神明选中的少女们谱写的童话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}神明选中的 总是天真无邪的少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而在大多数情况下 少女们的结局会是——
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要举例就是战舰长门
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.23,0:24:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.05,0:24:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.79,0:24:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太古怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.90,0:24:19.95,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}突击
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.05,0:24:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}玩真心话大冒险 喜欢的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还有园子在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.55,0:24:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}回家前都是合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.34,0:24:26.31,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}终点！
